  "title": "WELDING ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Welding Engineer Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Leading welding projects.</li><li>Analyzing engineering designs for welding requirements.</li><li>Overseeing a team of welders.</li><li>Reviewing welding procedures, processes, and documentation.</li><li>Managing welding procedure qualifications and generating welding procedures to help the welding teams.</li><li>Conducting failure analyses and cause analyses on welding issues.</li></ul><p><strong>Welding Engineer Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Previous experience in welding engineering.</li><li>Licensed Engineer.</li><li>Solid leadership skills.</li><li>Strong organizational and administrative skills.</li><li>Computer literate.</li></ul>",
